{
  "stem": "24409.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I was [GERMAN] assistant to a lawyer-- more than assistant, an apprentice-- who [INAUDIBLE] practically all the lawyers were too, in Salzburg, from the summer of 1931 to the summer of 1932.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there I was, in Salzburg, where there-- this was about the [? framework ?].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were elections in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Hitler came to give his speech at Rosenheim, which is a city in southern Bavaria, not far from Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to this, and that's where I saw Hitler speak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, I followed all the time, the rise after this-- the direction in which he won very many votes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Salzburg?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Salzburg the anti-Semitism was much stronger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's still there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's kept down to a minimum, during the Festspiele, when the tourists are coming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do not remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met my wife under very odd circumstances.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- usually I went to bed very late.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once a week, I had what I call [GERMAN], sleeping [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was going to bed early, around 7 o'clock or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was still, outside, light for a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was summer time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The watches were changed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when it started to get dark, I had-- hadn't fallen asleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I decided to go to the park for a walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I saw there, sitting on a chair, of a long row of empty chairs, my wife.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I looked at her and decided I would try to speak to her, and passed her, and came back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to get a response at all, I asked her the stupidest question-- excuse me, is this seat free?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, idiot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All these seats are free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With this, she had responded.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
